title: The Speed of Dark
description:
Torva Messor is a man who claims to be Death in the flesh. Currently trapped in a

mental facility for the elderly insane he is telling his story to whoever will 

listen. Immortality has been rampant for over three years and death is extinct. 

Trying to break out he enlists a crew of friends who are willing to help him so they 

too can finally die. Will he be able to break free of the facility or will he be 

trapped forever along with everyone else slowly going crazy?
